WEBVTT

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:08.759
Nothing much.

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:10.800
Just routine, a casual chat.

00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:12.880
Let's begin.

00:00:14.560 --> 00:00:15.400
Name.

00:00:15.919 --> 00:00:16.760
Luo Xiao.

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:18.359
Gender.

00:00:20.079 --> 00:00:20.920
Male.

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:28.679
What's your relationship with

00:00:29.079 --> 00:00:29.879
Fengmao Business Consulting Co., Ltd.?

00:00:30.239 --> 00:00:31.120
Legal counsel.

00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:33.119
What exactly do you handle?

00:00:34.679 --> 00:00:35.799
Specifically...

00:00:35.960 --> 00:00:37.000
well...

00:00:37.320 --> 00:00:38.359
Here, Bro Mao.

00:00:39.759 --> 00:00:40.479
Xiao.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:41.880
There's something

00:00:42.039 --> 00:00:43.280
I need you to think it through for me.

00:00:44.359 --> 00:00:45.759
Boss Chen.

00:00:46.240 --> 00:00:48.359
Bro Mao is Boss Chen's nickname.

00:00:48.439 --> 00:00:49.359
I know that much.

00:00:49.719 --> 00:00:50.920
Since I don't go to Fengmao often,

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:52.920
I don't see him much either.

00:00:53.280 --> 00:00:54.200
A Xin.

00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:56.159
The guy who drives the small van, remember?

00:00:56.520 --> 00:00:57.280
He's gone.

00:00:57.719 --> 00:00:58.640
Gone?

00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:00.600
Ran off?

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:01.799
Dead.

00:01:05.799 --> 00:01:08.359
Of course I know about Chen Yongjiang.

00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:10.640
But

00:01:11.599 --> 00:01:12.680
I'm a lawyer,

00:01:13.159 --> 00:01:14.799
not a magician.

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:18.200
How do you think you got this far?

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:20.359
That day...

00:01:20.760 --> 00:01:22.560
That day I went to ask for time off.

00:01:22.680 --> 00:01:23.719
Chen Yongjiang...

00:01:25.519 --> 00:01:26.680
Chen Yongjiang wasn't there, right?

00:01:39.879 --> 00:01:40.439
Over there.

00:01:40.519 --> 00:01:41.120
Yeah, that one.

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:41.920
That bag right there.

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:42.920
Yes, that bag.

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:44.680
It's pretty big.

00:01:45.280 --> 00:01:46.159
A fisherman.

00:01:46.439 --> 00:01:47.640
He hooked this bag in the water,

00:01:47.799 --> 00:01:49.280
pulled it up and found a body.

00:01:49.359 --> 00:01:50.120
Called the police right away.

00:01:51.959 --> 00:01:53.359
Check around the reservoir entrance.

00:01:53.599 --> 00:01:54.719
See if there's any dashcam footage.

00:01:55.079 --> 00:01:56.000
Call the forensics team right over.

00:01:56.079 --> 00:01:56.920
Have them take samples on-site.

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:57.680
Got it.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:06.599
Zhang Da.

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.240
We just pulled it out.

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:10.520
Good.

00:02:16.280 --> 00:02:17.039
What's his name?

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:18.039
Chen Guang.

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:19.000
How's the investigation going?

00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:19.840
Almost done.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:20.680
Good.

00:02:29.759 --> 00:02:30.439
Boss.

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:32.039
Forty-two pieces.

00:02:40.159 --> 00:02:41.240
The victim's name is Xin Qili,

00:02:41.759 --> 00:02:42.520
known as A Xin.

00:02:42.759 --> 00:02:44.240
Thirty-three years old, local.

00:02:44.719 --> 00:02:46.439
He was a freelance freight driver.

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.840
Used an old white van year-round

00:02:48.919 --> 00:02:50.199
to take on odd local delivery jobs.

00:02:50.879 --> 00:02:52.599
Mixed business, highly mobile.

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:54.520
Jailed six years ago for economic crimes,

00:02:55.080 --> 00:02:56.560
later released early

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:58.039
for good behavior.

00:02:59.240 --> 00:03:01.639
Footage near the reservoir shows

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:03.120
that night at 4:13,

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:04.639
a black MPV entered,

00:03:05.159 --> 00:03:06.680
and returned at 4:33.

00:03:07.400 --> 00:03:09.520
Initial screening of other vehicles

00:03:09.520 --> 00:03:10.319
shows no direct social ties

00:03:10.319 --> 00:03:11.840
with the victim.

00:03:12.919 --> 00:03:15.400
But this Fengmao Company,

00:03:16.240 --> 00:03:18.599
the victim had delivered small goods for them.

00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:20.599
That counts as financial dealings.

00:03:24.879 --> 00:03:26.159
Fengmao Company.

00:03:27.199 --> 00:03:28.960
Why does that ring a bell?

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:41.159
Weren't you the one who told Bro Mao

00:03:41.159 --> 00:03:42.840
to go find A Xin and sign that

00:03:42.919 --> 00:03:43.960
compensation agreement?

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:45.919
That's why Bro Mao went.

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:48.159
Who knew the punk would push his luck?

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:50.199
He demanded 200,000 from us.

00:03:50.960 --> 00:03:51.919
Bro Mao lost his temper.

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:53.080
Hit him a bit too hard.

00:03:54.759 --> 00:03:55.680
Ended up killing him.

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:57.599
At the time, I was

00:03:58.319 --> 00:03:59.280
drunk.

00:04:01.319 --> 00:04:03.199
So I just rushed to dispose of him.

00:04:03.879 --> 00:04:04.800
Grabbed a chainsaw,

00:04:04.960 --> 00:04:06.520
chopped him up right there.

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:08.560
Dumped him in the old reservoir.

00:04:09.280 --> 00:04:10.199
Didn't expect

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:11.439
the bag

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:13.080
didn't sink.

00:04:13.319 --> 00:04:14.400
It floated up.

00:04:18.279 --> 00:04:19.079
That's it.

00:04:19.639 --> 00:04:20.600
That's the whole story.

00:04:21.319 --> 00:04:22.160
So, you know,

00:04:22.839 --> 00:04:24.199
help your bro figure this out.

00:04:30.319 --> 00:04:31.120
Lawyer Luo.

00:04:32.279 --> 00:04:34.800
This whole thing started because of you.

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:38.600
You've got to take responsibility, right?

00:04:42.560 --> 00:04:43.879
How am I supposed to take responsibility?

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:47.240
I told A Xin to sign a contract.

00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:49.240
I didn't tell him to die!

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:50.920
That whole Fengmao mess,

00:04:51.279 --> 00:04:52.720
the case files in our records room

00:04:52.839 --> 00:04:53.920
could stack up into a pile.

00:04:54.519 --> 00:04:56.360
Private loans,

00:04:56.680 --> 00:04:58.560
contract disputes, violent collection.

00:04:59.160 --> 00:05:01.480
Goes on all year round.

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:02.720
Boss.

00:05:03.399 --> 00:05:05.519
I remember Fengmao's lawyer

00:05:05.920 --> 00:05:06.920
is your brother-in-law, right?

00:05:10.680 --> 00:05:11.439
Wife's sister's husband.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:12.800
Let's go.

00:05:13.399 --> 00:05:14.079
Where to?

00:05:14.199 --> 00:05:15.079
A trip to Fengmao.

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:16.680
Ah Kai.

00:05:36.319 --> 00:05:37.759
Let's turn ourselves in.

00:05:39.720 --> 00:05:40.560
While we still can.

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:42.120
The motive,

00:05:42.399 --> 00:05:43.839
and evidence are all still pretty clear.

00:05:44.120 --> 00:05:45.519
I can pull some strings.

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:47.839
Try to get it classified as

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:50.000
a crime of passion from a dispute.

00:05:50.120 --> 00:05:51.079
Or maybe

00:05:51.439 --> 00:05:52.360
manslaughter.

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:53.920
We can describe

00:05:53.920 --> 00:05:55.480
how you lost control while drunk.

00:05:55.759 --> 00:05:56.800
Plus you turning yourself in.

00:05:57.360 --> 00:05:58.839
Within the legal framework right now,

00:05:58.839 --> 00:06:00.360
this is the only

00:06:00.680 --> 00:06:01.680
chance for leniency,

00:06:03.560 --> 00:06:04.800
the only way to save your life.

00:06:07.079 --> 00:06:08.040
Save my life?

00:06:09.079 --> 00:06:10.439
Rot in prison until I die?

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:14.639
Is there any other way?

00:06:15.399 --> 00:06:16.000
Well,

00:06:16.680 --> 00:06:17.319
then,

00:06:18.319 --> 00:06:19.560
the only option is to run.

00:06:23.240 --> 00:06:23.879
You

00:06:24.480 --> 00:06:25.519
You said just now

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.519
where were you and your daughter going?

00:06:27.920 --> 00:06:28.639
Bro Mao.

00:06:31.040 --> 00:06:31.920
We're all in this life together,

00:06:32.439 --> 00:06:33.680
we're brothers, right?

00:06:34.759 --> 00:06:36.360
Today your bro's hit a wall.

00:06:36.959 --> 00:06:38.680
Help your bro out.

00:06:38.879 --> 00:06:40.759
Bro Mao, this time is really different.

00:06:41.279 --> 00:06:42.480
This, this is murder.

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:44.199
I'm a lawyer, I can't...

00:06:52.439 --> 00:06:53.560
We're friends.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:55.920
You help me escape,

00:06:57.759 --> 00:06:59.160
that's the only way you stay alive.

00:07:01.079 --> 00:07:02.040
You get it?

00:07:04.079 --> 00:07:05.680
I'm not forcing you.

00:07:06.959 --> 00:07:08.319
Your bro just doesn't want to die.

00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:11.720
I'm not involved.

00:07:14.680 --> 00:07:15.800
Like hell you aren't.

00:07:18.879 --> 00:07:20.600
So get your head straight.

00:07:22.600 --> 00:07:24.079
We're in the same boat.

00:07:25.759 --> 00:07:26.680
Careful, careful.

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:42.079
This won't work.

00:07:42.879 --> 00:07:43.600
Can't lie here.

00:07:43.839 --> 00:07:44.759
Too easy to get spotted.

00:07:45.959 --> 00:07:46.879
Can't let anyone see you.

00:07:47.199 --> 00:07:47.839
Okay.

00:08:00.959 --> 00:08:02.439
I'll leave that jacket for you as a pillow.

00:08:03.079 --> 00:08:04.040
Watch your head, bro.

00:08:05.279 --> 00:08:06.360
Bro, I'll grab you some water for the road.

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:07.120
Get back here.

00:08:07.519 --> 00:08:08.519
Don't let the cops see you.

00:08:08.759 --> 00:08:09.680
Hurry up and close the lid.

00:08:10.480 --> 00:08:10.879
Got it.

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:11.680
Closing it now, bro.

00:08:30.959 --> 00:08:31.720
Brother-in-law.

00:08:32.679 --> 00:08:33.679
What are you doing here?

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:35.840
I... I was working.

00:08:37.399 --> 00:08:38.120
I'm done now.

00:08:38.600 --> 00:08:39.879
Just dropping off some documents.

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:41.559
And you guys are...

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:42.960
working on a case?

00:08:43.960 --> 00:08:44.720
Uncle!

00:08:44.960 --> 00:08:45.639
Paopao!

00:08:45.759 --> 00:08:47.080
You're working today too?

00:08:49.840 --> 00:08:51.039
You're out working,

00:08:51.039 --> 00:08:52.279
and you brought Paopao along?

00:08:52.840 --> 00:08:53.600
Well, today...

00:08:53.679 --> 00:08:55.399
I'm taking her to Donglan to play.

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:57.639
So I dropped off the documents early,

00:08:57.720 --> 00:08:58.720
so I won't have to come back.

00:09:00.639 --> 00:09:01.279
Paopao,

00:09:01.559 --> 00:09:02.399
where's your backpack?

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:04.480
Mommy got me a day off

00:09:04.639 --> 00:09:05.879
so I can have fun.